name: Dysfunctional Unicorn Nft Collection By Coops 01/08
description: Hey and welcome to the Dysfunctional Unicorn (DU) family! DU 01 is the first born of her triplet sisters. She always has been jealous of her sisters better looks, but she has a heart of rainbow. She is an Augmented Reality DU, so she loves to be copy and pasted and used in selfies on instagram stories and snapchat. She's looking for a friend to share her love with today, and she has a lot to give <3 <3 <3 <3 <3
